RecentItemsHandler: This class is created to implement recent items. The method updateRIList is called by MainAreaBackingBean and MainAreaHandler through contextual events registered as NOTIFY_RI_LIST in UIShell. Create by: Vik (Xteam) Creation Date: 13-Oct-2008

updateRIList

public void updateRIList(FndMethodParameters methodParameters)
This method is called as a result of contextual event raised by UIShell whenever there is a manipulation in UIShell stack This api adds the current taskflow to the recent items cache in session. The cache contains only the list of taskflows accessed within the current session and within the current application. On Session expiration or cross app navigation, the list has to be persisted to the persistance store.
